CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Immunic Inc is a clinical stage biopharmaceutical company developing a pipeline of selective oral immunology therapies aimed at treating chronic inflammatory and autoimmune diseases, including ulcerative colitis, Crohn's disease, relapsing remitting multiple sclerosis, and psoriasis. The company is developing three small molecule products, IMU-838 is a selective immune modulator that inhibits the intracellular metabolism of activated immune cells by blocking the enzyme DHODH, IMU-935 is an inverse agonist of RORyt and IMU-856 targets the restoration of the intestinal barrier function.
